messages.message: hi engineering! Happy Monday. To help us identify work that requires doc updates or new docs, we have a new *Docs* section in our Jira projects. Select the *Docs > TODO* checkbox to let me know about your awesome work that needs technical content. Please tell your teammates and their teammates and so on and so on. Thanks @Heymian for the back work in Atlassian Jira. As a reminder, see the *Docs workflow (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DOCS/pages/210665492/Docs+workflow)* description on the wiki.
